Class Octree

java.lang.Object
  Quadtree
      Octree

public class Octree
extends Quadtree

The Octree class defines a three dimensional binary tree. Each node references a octant. The root node references a octant that encompasses all other sub-octants.

Author:
Christopher Glasz
